Package org.elasticsearch.xpack.sql.expression.function.scalar.whitelist

Class InternalSqlScriptUtils

java.lang.Object
org.elasticsearch.xpack.ql.expression.function.scalar.whitelist.InternalQlScriptUtils
org.elasticsearch.xpack.sql.expression.function.scalar.whitelist.InternalSqlScriptUtils
Direct Known Subclasses:
InternalScriptUtils
public class InternalSqlScriptUtils extends InternalQlScriptUtils
Whitelisted class for SQL scripts. Acts as a registry of the various static methods used internally by the scalar functions (to simplify the whitelist definition).
